The scope of the study group shall be as follows: -
i. Simplification of procedures with a view to provide notified services to the citizens more easily and
Re-engineering the government process to streamline it.
Creating an ii.Common application form.
Developing procedures for attaching services to iii.Digi-locker.
iv. Fixation of time limit for preservation of records in respect of notified services.
v. Some other services in the field office under the Department of Cultural Affairs State
